{"tid":149931,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"曾打針5歲童染侵入性肺炎球菌亡 今年首宗","createTime":"2017-03-09T15:36:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-10T09:27:15.000Z","uid":51469,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2ef4d950c2f6b55593f6588a2a216f954f51e4e4","tid":149931,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T15:36:09.000Z","msg":"衞生防護中心接獲今年首宗侵入性肺炎球菌病的死亡個案。不幸死亡的5歲男童過往健康良好，他自上月10日起出現發燒、咳嗽和氣促等病徵，上月13日入住將軍澳醫院，同日轉送瑪嘉烈醫院兒科深切治療部，本月5日再送往瑪麗醫院兒科深切治療部接受進一步治療，昨日死亡。<br />\n<br />\n病人是香港人，曾接種肺炎球菌疫苗。臨床診斷為敗血病和肺炎併發膿胸及氣胸。病人於上月13日抽取的血液樣本經化驗後證實對肺炎鏈球菌（肺炎球菌）呈陽性反應。<br />\n<br />\n初步調查顯示，男童最近沒有外遊，家居接觸亦沒有出現病徵。他就讀的幼稚園至今沒有其他同類個案或爆發的報告，生防護中心已向校方提供預防呼吸道傳染病的建議。據了解，男童就讀香港幼稚園協會幼兒學校。 <br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170309/56402902\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170309%2F56402902&d=iLyAB%2BOE6twWPMF9W2uC6i7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=48c0d3ef\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170309%2F56402902&h=5b94d25f\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170309/56402902</a><br />\n打完針都中招?"},{"pid":"59f31b1f2afaf9760bdcd51bd4c6faa793fe2f36","tid":149931,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T16:12:17.000Z","msg":"假針<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"576ca7321e0c4e0bcd72f8542da0da23cefc0309","tid":149931,"uid":61271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T16:18:48.000Z","msg":"你不如問點解食左藥都死?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有咩係100%?"},{"pid":"a7aea037d134b5f27b1a8ddf5c96be608219f87e","tid":149931,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T23:23:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你不如問點解食左藥都死?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有咩係100%?</blockquote><br />\n哦"},{"pid":"0d20